__pycache__/
    .ipynb_checkpoints/
    *.csv
    .env
    ```

### Step 3: Stage and Commit Locally
Tell Git to track these files:

```bash
# Add all files to the staging area
git add .

# Commit them with a professional message
git commit -m "Initial commit: Telco churn prediction with XGBoost and SHAP explainability"
